review: Dr. Bharat is very insightful and is gifted with good clinical acumen. My mother was suffering a lot and experiencing great pain and discomfort because of some structure damage from an older implant(made by another dentist), and Dr. Bharat corrected it very quickly in few minutes. His work is also very professional and respectful towards the patient.He saves all the patient's profile in his laptop and explains very clearly the issues and how the treatment would help. I am very pleased and thankful both for his diagnosis and prognosis. Definitely would recommend this doctor!!

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I visited Dr Bharat Reddy for my father's concern of teeth sensitivity. The doc had examined him and suggested and full teeth x-ray. Thankfully the hospital is desently equipped with all the required equipments as the patient doesn't have to run around some diagnostic center for such requirements. Immediately after examining the x-ray, the doc explained us which all teeth had the issue and which require RCT done immediately. The planning of schedule every week from there on was well done and the required treatment was done. The support staff is also very courteous and well organized. In these days it was a pleasant surprise to find that there are still some docs who value their Hippocratic Oath! Thankyou once again Dr Bharat Reddy!!
